ynamic client registration. Its clientId, client_credentials\ngrant, and redirect URI allowlist are server-managed — admins editing it\nthrough the settings UI can only break the DCR flow (and already did, per\nthe 409s surfacing on PUT earlier in this branch).\n\n- modifyGetObjectList filters the list endpoint so the system registrar\n  never appears in the UI\n- preUpdateEntity / preDeleteEntity reject any attempt to touch it by\n  clientId match, even if the uid is known\n- Direct GET /oAuth2Clients/{uid} still works so server-side callers and\n  DCR itself can read the record\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\nSigned-off-by: Morten Svanaes \u003cmsvanaes@dhis2.org\u003e","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"606926ece9148f627bab29508003c6caa8d91381","tree_id":"4ea168bbb785d2ea8810ed1e9e66d2683806beb4","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:03:28Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptio